    "Description": "One of our Clips put out a kill order on a <EM4>~mission(AmbushTarget)</EM4>. Feel like making \u2018em happy by taking it out?\n\nHere\u2019s what you need to know. The target and their escort are scheduled to pass by <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. Looks like there\u2019s an emission cloud nearby that can hide your ship\u2019s sig. Wait there until you\u2019re ready to strike. \n\nThe Clip only cares about wiping out the target. Anything of value you find floating in the wreckage is all yours. \n\nAnd on top of that, I'll give the main contractor a bonus <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount)</EM4> Council Scrip to sweeten the pot. \n\n- Stows",
